@60029 = ~Wand of Sleep~
@60030 = ~This wand will emit a gold beam of energy at its targets up to a maximum range of 80 ft., affecting a 15-ft. radius. If the target creatures fail their Save vs. Wand, they will fall into a deep, comatose sleep for %duration%.

