(Invocation/Evocation)

Charge abilities:
– Spook
  Target flees at maximum speed as far from the wielder as possible
  Range: 30 ft.
  Area of Effect: 1 creature
  Duration: 3 rounds
  Saving Throw: Saving vs. Wand negates

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~


